# 2. Raw Data

## Data Acquisition
The dataset was obtained as a CSV file:
US Cancer Death Rates by State Machine.csv
It contains cancer death rates per 100,000 people for each U.S. state from 2014 to 2023 and total deaths for the same years as well.

## Data Source
I got the data from: https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/state-stats/deaths/cancer.html
